    <abstract>
      <t>[RFC8955] defines BGP flow specification version 1 (FSv1) and
   [I-D.ietf-idr-flowspec-v2] defines BGP flow specification (FSv2)
   protocol.  This document proposes extensions to BGP Flow
   Specification Version 2 to support MPLS-based EVPN traffic filtering.</t>
